***********************************************
Steps to check / fix Switchwire gantry movement
***********************************************

1. In Klipper printer.cfg add:

    [force_move]
    enable_force_move: True

Save and restart.

2. Put the tool head in the middle of the gantry both on X and Z.

3. In Klipper command prompt execute the following:

    SET_KINEMATIC_POSITION X=125 Z=100
    G91

Then

    G0 X5

Note in which way it moved.

Then

    G0 Z5

Note what way it moved.

Compare the result with the graph in SW motor configuration guide and configure or swap motor connections properly:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/VoronDesign/Voron-Documentation/main/build/startup/images/SW-motor-configuration-guide.png
